      <title>世界银行向赞比亚提供 2 亿美元用于抗击干旱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/world-bank-gives-zambia-200-million-for-drought-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据赞比亚财政部声明称，世界银行已批准向赞比亚再提供 2 亿美元赠款，帮助该国应对数十年来最严重的干旱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/world-bank-gives-zambia-200-million-for-drought-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:14:22 GMT</pubDate>
