    <item>
      <title>估计法国左翼计划的成本将是马克龙计划的六倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-left-s-plans-to-cost-six-times-macron-s-estimates-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最新估算，参加法国立法议会选举的各政党做出的竞选承诺在成本上差异巨大，其中左翼联盟的承诺成本最高，主要体现在降低退休年龄的计划上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-left-s-plans-to-cost-six-times-macron-s-estimates-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，嘉能可因报价不及格而撤回对 Kazzinc 的出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/glencore-said-to-withdraw-kazzinc-sale-after-offers-fall-short</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，嘉能可公司已放弃出售其在哈萨克斯坦矿业公司 Kazzinc 的股份的计划，因为潜在买家未能匹配其估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/glencore-said-to-withdraw-kazzinc-sale-after-offers-fall-short</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
